## Example prompts

### Phase 1: Triage

```
@confluence-analyzer.mdc Run Phase 1 on _data/confluence_pages.json. Triage and categorize each page, suggest tags and white-label checklist, output backlog.
```

```
@confluence-analyzer.mdc Run Phase 1 on the Confluence export but only for pages whose title or labels mention "Canvas" or "Liquid".
```

### Phase 2: Draft

```
@confluence-analyzer.mdc Run Phase 2 for the top 5 pages from the Phase 1 backlog. White-label and draft use case library entries with tags and links to relevant docs.
```

```
@confluence-analyzer.mdc Run Phase 2 for the page with id 258150072. Generalize the content and add it to the use case library.
```
